## Recruiter Note

This repo demonstrates **behavioral system design using smart contract architecture** — mapping a psychological process (shadow integration) to contract state, event emission, and enforced sequencing. Part of the [Future Systems Lab](https://github.com/Future-Systems-Lab) ecosystem.

---

## What This Is

We all carry limiting beliefs that keep us from living to our full potential — mental programs written in childhood, trauma, or fear that run silently in the background. What if you could reprogram them? What if letting go of what no longer serves you wasn't just a therapeutic concept, but a tangible digital act?

**AlchemistForge** combines digital psychology with blockchain technology to help you transmute pain into purpose. This isn't just mental health innovation — it's your easy introduction to cryptocurrency, done through something deeply meaningful: releasing old beliefs and literally sending that energy back to the universe via code.

You'll learn blockchain by actually using it. No confusing jargon. No finance lectures. Just a simple ritual: name what you're letting go of, transmute it into your new truth, and celebrate. The smart contract does the rest, recording your transformation permanently across thousands of computers worldwide.

This is the future of mental wellness meeting the future of technology. And you can participate in 10 minutes.

---

## Why It Matters

There's power in **witnessed permanence**. Your transformation isn't stored on some company's server — it lives on thousands of computers worldwide, permanent and unchangeable. Jung called this "integrating the shadow": not erasing wounds, but incorporating them into a larger self.

---

## The Code

```solidity
contract AlchemistForge {
    mapping(address => string) public purpose;

    function alchemize(string calldata _pain) external {
        purpose[msg.sender] = _pain;
        emit Transmuted(msg.sender, _pain);
    }

    function celebrateEgregiously() external {
        require(bytes(purpose[msg.sender]).length > 0, "Cast your pain first.");
        emit Celebrated(msg.sender);
    }
}
```

**What it does:** Write your transformation with `alchemize`. Celebrate with `celebrateEgregiously` — but only after you've done the work. You can't skip steps. The blockchain enforces what therapy teaches: celebration comes after processing pain.

---

## Quick Start (10 Minutes)

1. **Get MetaMask** — Install from [metamask.io](https://metamask.io), create wallet, save recovery phrase
2. **Switch to Sepolia** — Open MetaMask → networks → enable test networks → select Sepolia
3. **Get free test crypto** — [sepoliafaucet.com](https://sepoliafaucet.com)
4. **Visit AlchemistForge** — [Click here](https://testnet.routescan.io/address/0xE092336F8f5082e57CcBb341A110C20ad186A324)
5. **Connect wallet** — "Contract" tab → "Write Contract" → "Connect Wallet"
6. **Alchemize** — Type your transformation → click Write → confirm
7. **Celebrate** — Click `celebrateEgregiously` → confirm

